---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Work with me - hellointernet.lol">
  <div class="content-block">
    <h1>Work with me</h1>

    <div class="content">
      <p>I work with people who recognize friction and want it removed.</p>
      <p><em>Not managed.</em></p>
      <p><strong>Gone.</strong></p>

      <p>
        This usually starts with something that’s slowing you down:
        <ul>
          <li>a messy process, a missing tool</li>
          <li>a decision that needs structure</li>
          <li>a system that’s quietly blocking progress</li>
        </ul>
      </p>

      <p>
        I help by building the thing that removes the constraint,
        then stepping back.
      </p>

      <h2>Good fit if</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>You have a real problem, but the solution isn’t obvious</li>
        <li>You need something built that doesn’t fit a standard template</li>
        <li>You’re tired of tools that create more work than they solve</li>
        <li>You have the authority to decide and the urgency to move</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Not a fit if</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>You want long discovery processes with no output</li>
        <li>You’re shopping for tools without a clear problem</li>
        <li>The work requires endless alignment meetings</li>
        <li>“Building” means talking about building</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How to start</h2>

      <p>
        Send an email that includes:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>What’s not working</li>
        <li>What good looks like</li>
        <li>When you need it by</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        If it’s a fit, we’ll talk.
        If it’s not, I’ll tell you quickly.
      </p>

      <div class="contact">
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong>
          <a href="mailto:joshua@fullyautomated.enterprises">joshua@fullyautomated.enterprises</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>


<style>
  .content-block {
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .content {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .content ul {
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .content li {
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .contact {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .contact p {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .contact strong {
    color: var(--text-dimmer);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
